sourcesContent:
let focusedHistoryContainer = {
  backgroundColor: "white", 
  width: "97%", 
  border: "1px solid #4382BC",
  margin: "22px auto 0px auto",
  overflowY: "scroll",
  overflowX: "hidden",
  height: "20%"
}

let focusedDivider = {
  height: "1px",
  width: "97%",
  margin: "0px auto 5px auto",
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC"
}

let focusedContainer = {
  width: "100%", 
  marginTop: "35px", 
  height: "88%", 
  border: "1px solid #4382BC",
  backgroundColor: "#e8fefd"
}

let focusedMainTitleContainer = {
  width: "100%", 
  height: "25px",
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  color: "white",
  fontSize: "17px",
  textAlign: "center",
  paddingTop: "3px",
  display: "flex",
  flexDirection: "row",
}

let focusedMainTitle = {
  width: "100%",
  lineHeight: "20px"
}

let focusedClose = {
  userSelect: "none", 
  fontSize: "25px", 
  cursor: "pointer", 
  lineHeight: "17px", 
  width: "auto", 
  transform: "rotate(45deg)", 
  marginRight: "6px",
  marginLeft: "auto"
} 

let focusedOtherTitle = {
  width: "100%",
  textAlign: "center",
  marginTop: "5px"
}

export {
  focusedHistoryContainer,
  focusedDivider,
  focusedContainer,
  focusedMainTitleContainer,
  focusedMainTitle,
  focusedClose,
  focusedOtherTitle
}
